videos.description: Bam Adebayo thinks he sees an open teammate, but he passes to Gabe Vincent, who's going from the bench to the scorer's table.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bam accidentally passes to teammate who's out of bounds) 2021/1/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam accidentally passes to teammate who's out of bounds

videos.description: James Harden comes up with the steal and races down the court to flush home a two-handed dunk for the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden turns steal into easy fast-break bucket) 2021/01/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden turns steal into easy fast-break bucket

videos.description: Bam Adebayo pulls up to bank in a shot from 3-point range to beat the buzzer at the end of the third quarter, giving the Heat a 71-70 lead over the Nets.
videos.headline: Adebayo banks in buzzer-beater

videos.description: After some early offensive struggles, the Nets go on a 15-0 run in the fourth quarter en route to defeating the Heat 98-85.
